ELonger-term%20effects%20could%20include%20a%20complete%20reversal%20of%20globalization%20and%20even%20a%20collapse%20of%20the%20WTO%2C%20according%20to%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics'%20Julius%20Sen.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWashington's%20penchant%20for%20wielding%20the%20dollar's%20global%20sway%20as%20an%20economic%20weapon%20has%20spooked%20countries%20from%20China%20and%20Brazil%2C%20fueling%20an%20unprecedented%20campaign%20to%20dethrone%20the%20greenback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdedollarization-faces-headwinds-argentina-dollar-zooms-5000-percent-vs-peso-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededollarization%20drive%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20all%20%E2%80%93%20some%20experts%20have%20been%20warning%20of%20this%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lse.ac.uk%2Fideas%2FAssets%2FDocuments%2Fupdates%2FLSE-IDEAS-Weaponisation-Dollar.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2019%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20political%20economy%20expert%20Julius%20Sen%20explored%20the%20way%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20weaponized%20the%20dollar%20by%20scrapping%20the%20Iran%20nuclear%20agreement%20signed%20in%202015.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20US%20slapped%20a%20number%20of%20sanctions%20on%20Tehran%20for%20failing%20to%20curb%20its%20nuclear%20program%2C%20including%20restrictions%20on%20the%20country's%20use%20of%20the%20greenback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20term%20'weaponization'%20is%20also%20apt%20as%20it%20explains%20how%20a%20relatively%20neutral%20but%20essential%20facility%20%E2%80%93%20the%20dollar%20and%20its%20accompanying%20payment%20system%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20powerful%20weapon%20by%20one%20UN%20member%20state%20against%20another%20withou