%20senior%20Chinese%20officials%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20he%20oversees%20reported%20anomalous%20activity%20to%20Microsoft%20that%20the%20tech%20firm%20later%20blamed%20on%20China-based%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Blinken's%20second%20try%20at%20making%20the%20high-profile%20trip.%20His%20first%20attempt%20in%20February%20was%20derailed%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20by%20the%20discovery%20of%20an%20alleged%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%20floating%20above%20the%20US%20-%20which%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20ordered%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20staying%20the%20course%20on%20its%20China-engagement%20strategy%2C%20continuing%20the%20string%20of%20contact%20with%20Beijing%20that%20began%20with%20Blinken.%20But%20the%20hacking%20episode%20underlines%20the%20growing%20risks%20of%20restarting%20crucial%20diplomatic%20engagement%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20when%20geopolitical%20competition%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20remains%20as%20fierce%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinken's%20trip%20last%20month%20-%20the%20most%20senior%20US%20delegation%20to%20China%20in%20five%20years%20-%20was%20only%20the%20first%20of%20several%20visits%20aimed%20at%20trying%20to%20re-establish%20more%20durable%20diplomatic%20links%20that%20China%20mostly%20severed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20then%20House%20Speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi's%20controversial%20stop%20in%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20responded%20to%20Pelosi's%20trip%20by%20holding%20unprecedented%20military%20drills%20around%20Taiwan.%20Similar%20exercises%20were%20held%20in%20April%2C%20when%20Taiwan's%20leader%2C%20Tsai%20Ing-wen%2C%20met%20House%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20they%20get%20to%20decide%20whether%20they're%20gonna%20do%20these%20meetings%20or%20not%2C%20and%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20feeling%20they%20want%20to%20put%20some%20skin%20in%20the%20game%20to%20see%20where%20this%20can%20lead%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christopher%20Johnson%2C%20the%20president%20of%20China%20Strategies%20Group%2C%20a%20political%20risk%20consultancy%2C%20and%20a%20former%20senior%20China%20analyst%20at%20the%20Central%20Intelligence%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20something%20really%20significant%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20like%20a%20mash-up%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20or%20something%20bad%2C%20then%20obviously%20that%20would%20be%20it.%20But%20I%20think%20garden-variety%20cyber%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20shown%20a%20similar%20commitment.%20Beijing%20shrugged%20off%20Biden's%20reference%20to%20Xi%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%26quot%3B%20days%20after%20Blinken's%20visit%2C%20still%20welcoming%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen%20in%20China%20weeks%20later.%20US%20climate%20envoy%20John%20Kerry%20is%20set%20to%20arrive%20in%20Beijing%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlinken%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20hacking%20on%20Thursday%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20China's%20top%20foreign%20policy%20official%20Wang%20Yi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20an%20Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20foreign%20ministers%20meeting%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20a%20senior%20State%20Department%20official%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20wouldn't%20say%20if%20Blinken%20had%20raised%20the%20latest%20incident%2C%20which%20included%20the%20alleged%20breach%20of%20the%20email%20account%20of%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Gina%20Raimondo.%20Before%20the%20revelations%2C%20she'd%20been%20both%20one%20of%20those%20seeking%20to%20visit%20China%20as%20part%20of%20the%20engagement%20efforts%20and%20a%20leading%20figure%20in%20the%20administration's%20moves%20to%20limit%20Beijing's%20access%20to%20high-tech%20semiconductors%20and%20chip-making%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hack%20that%20was%20revealed%20this%20week%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsophisticated%26quot%3B%20example%20of%20China's%20increasingly%20advanced%20cyber%20abilities%2C%20according%20to%20George%20Barnes%2C%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20US%20National%20Security%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%26quot%3Byet%20another%20example%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20around%20us%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20conference%20of%20intelligence%20professionals%20in%20Maryland%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BChina%20is%20steadfast%20and%20determined%20to%20penetrate%20our%20government%2C%20our%20companies%2C%20our%20critical%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20routinely%20accuses%20the%20US%20of%20hacking.%20The%20Foreign%20Ministry%20in%20Beijing%20this%20week%20called%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20biggest%20hacking%20empire%20and%20global%20cyber%20thief%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20for%20Washington%20to%20explain%20its%20own%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Zombie%20Engagement'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20continuing%20current%20of%20irritants%20in%20the%20relationship%20with%20China%2C%20Republican%20lawmakers%20have%20stepped%20up%20criticism%20of%20Biden's%20diplomatic%20strategy.%20Mike%20Gallagher%2C%20who%20chairs%20a%20House%20select%20committee%20on%20competition%20with%20China%2C%20derides%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bzombie%20engagement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Gallagher's%20committee%20announced%20a%20hearing%20next%20week%20on%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20China%20strategy%20that%20will%20see%20will%20see%20three%20senior%20policy%20appointees%20appear%20as%20witnesses%3A%20Ely%20Ratner%2C%20the%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20defense%20for%20Indo-Pacific%20security%20affairs%3B%20Daniel%20Kritenbrink%2C%20the%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20state%20for%20East%20Asian%20and%20Pacific%20affairs%3B%20and%20Thea%20Rozman%20Kendler%2C%20the%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20commerce%20for%20export%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Michael%20McCaul%2C%20a%20Texas%20Republican%20who%20chairs%20the%20House%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Committee%2C%20issued%20a%20subpoena%20to%20Blinken%20for%20documents%20related%20to%20the%20administration's%20moves%20against%20China.%20Using%20the%20abbreviation%20for%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China%2C%20he%20accused%20the%20State%20Department%20of%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20weakness%20and%20passivity%20in%20the%20face%20of%20PRC%20aggression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20rejects%20that%20criticism%2C%20highlighting%20the%20numerous%20sanctions%20and%20other%20export%20controls%20that%20it's%20imposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20we%20heard%20over%20and%20over%20from%20Chinese%20officials%20is%20their%20deep%20protests%20and%20their%20deep%20complaints%20about%20the%20competitive%20actions%20that%20we%20have%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E--%20With%20assistance%20from%20Peter%20Martin.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689334740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fnl0te4c4_biden-xi-650_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-manoeuvers-around-another-china-spy-row-to-improve-ties-4207461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20June%2016%2C%20the%20same%20day%20Antony%20Blinken%20was%20set%20to%20fly%20to%20Beijing%20for%20meetings%20with%20senior%20Chinese%20officials%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20he%20oversees%20reported%20anomalous%20activity%20to%20Microsoft%20that%20the%20tech%20firm%20later%20blamed%20on%20China-based%20hackers.%22%2C%22