0bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b034349751e3001929fe14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcdonald%20and%20Jivan%20in%20one%20of%20the%2070s-inspired%20bedrooms.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Qaid%20Jivan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20paid%20%241.45%20million%20for%20the%20house%20and%20estimated%20that%20we'd%20spend%20around%20%24150%2C000%20on%20renovations.%20But%20we%20challenged%20ourselves%20to%20spend%20under%20%245%2C000%20to%20turn%20the%20space%20we%20planned%20to%20use%20for%20our%20AirBnB%C2%A0%20into%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment.%20Here's%20exactly%20what%20we%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20did%20most%20of%20the%20work%20ourselves%20and%20only%20did%20what%20was%20necessary%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-renovation-cost-each-room-2019-6%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20renovate%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20AirBnB%20space%20mostly%20on%20our%20own%20and%20with%20friends%20to%20save%20labor%20costs.%20We%20did%20hire%20a%20contractor%20to%20fix%20up%20the%20bathroom%20and%20paid%20around%20%242%2C700%20for%20a%20new%20toilet%2C%20shower%20kit%2C%20and%20fixtures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20we%20saved%20money%20was%20by%20not%20installing%20a%20full%20kitchen%20in%20the%20space.%20Having%20to%20build%20out%20plumbing%20for%20that%20could%20have%20cost%20more%20than%20%245%2C000.%20Instead%2C%20we%20installed%20a%20kitchenette%20which%20cost%20under%20%24200.%20Since%20most%20of%20our%20guests%20stay%20for%20an%20average%20of%202.5%20nights%2C%20we've%20found%20that%20this%20equipment%20is%20enough%20for%20them%20to%20make%20quick%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchenette.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b046ba9751e300192a0263%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJivan%20and%20McDo