20wicket%2C%20which%20the%20highest%20opening%20stand%20for%20India%20in%20Tests%20outside%20Asia.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20first%20instance%20when%20India%20took%20the%20lead%20without%20losing%20a%20wicket%2C%20after%20having%20dismissed%20West%20Indies%20for%20150%20on%20Day%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20unbeaten%20knock%2C%20Jaiswal%20scripted%20multiple%20feats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20For%20the%20record%2C%20he%20faced%20350%20balls%20by%20stumps%20on%20Day%202%2C%20the%20most%20by%20an%20Indian%20in%20an%20innings%20on%20Test%20debut.%C2%A0The%20previous%20best%20was%20322%20balls%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Azharuddin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40063-mohammad-azizuddin-azharuddin-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Azharuddin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20his%20110%20against%20England%20at%20Eden%20Gardens%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Jaiswal's%20143%20is%20also%20the%20highest%20individual%20score%20by%20an%20Indian%20on%20debut%20away%20from%20home%20in%20the%20longest%20format.%20The%20previous%20highest%20was%20Sourav%20Ganguly's%20131%20against%20England%20on%20debut%20in%201996%20at%20Lord's%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20The%2021-year-old%20also%20became%20the%2017th%20Indian%20cricketer%20to%20score%20a%20century%20on%20Test%20debut.%20The%20first%20Indian%20to%20score%20a%20ton%20on%20his%20Test%20debut%20was%20Lala%20Amarnath%2C%20way%20back%20in%201933%20against%20England%2C%20while%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20was%20the%20last%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat%20back%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Jaiswal%20also%20became%20only%20the%20third%20opener%20to%20hit%20a%20century%20on%20debut.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20fifth%20Indian%20to%20score%20a%20ton%20on%20his%20debut%20overseas%20after%20Shikhar%20Dhawan%20(vs%20Australia%2C%20Mohali%2C%202013)%20and%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20(vs%20WI%2C%20Rajkot%2C%202018).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Jaiswal%20was%20delighted%20after%20scoring%20his%20maiden%20Test%20ton%20and%20said%20this%20is%20just%20the%20%26quot%3Bstart%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20revealed%20how%20captain%20Rohit's%20words%20of%20wisdom%20motivated%20him%20to%20do%20well%20on%20his%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20the%20start%20of%20my%20career...%20Koshish%20yeh%20karoonga%20ki%20main%20kitna%20lamba%20leke%20jaa%20sakta%20hoon%20(My%20effort%20will%20be%20to%20see%20how%20far%20would%20I%20be%20able%20to%20take%20it%20from%20here)%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689324720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ft50esusg_yashasvi-jaiswal-afp_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-1st-test-five-milestones-yashasvi-jaiswal-set-en-route-to-maiden-test-century-4206264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20was%20delighted%20after%20scoring%20his%20maiden%20Test%20ton%20and%20said%20this%20is%20just%20the%20%26quot%3Bstart%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-1st-test-five-milestones-yashasvi-jaiswal-set-en-route-to-maiden-test-century-4206264%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-1st-test-five-milestones-yashasvi-jaiswal-set-en-route-to-maiden-test-century-4206264%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-1st-test-five-milestones-yashasvi-jaiswal-set-en-route-to-maiden-test-century-4206264%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eighth%20Cheetah%20found%20dead%20in%20Kuno%20National%20Park%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689324405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101753391%2C