tyle%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fhealth-risks-associated-with-overflowing-of-yamuna-in-delhi-heres-what-you-can-do%2Farticleshow%2F101752528.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LA%20police%20chief%20criticises%20officer%20who%20punched%20woman%20twice%20while%20holding%20baby%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689323280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-los-angeles-police_6218401.jpg%3F20230714093648%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fla-police-chief-criticises-officer-who-punched-woman-twice-in-face-while-holding-baby-12920826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20sheriff%20has%20said%20an%20incident%20where%20a%20police%20officer%20punched%20a%20woman%20twice%20in%20the%20face%20while%20she%20held%20her%20three-week-old%20baby%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unacceptable%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fla-police-chief-criticises-officer-who-punched-woman-twice-in-face-while-holding-baby-12920826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fla-police-chief-criticises-officer-who-punched-woman-twice-in-face-while-holding-baby-12920826%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fla-police-chief-criticises-officer-who-punched-woman-twice-in-face-while-holding-baby-12920826%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%202004%20vs%202024%20-%20Why%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20May%20Not%20Help%20Opposition%20Efforts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20bid%20to%20reconstruct%20the%20almost%20defunct%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20and%20a%20possible%20rejuvenation%20of%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20next%20week%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20start%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament.%20The%20two%20alliances%2C%20each%20pivoting%20around%20lead%20players%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20will%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20for%20the%20next%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20host%20the%20follow-up%20of%20the%20Patna%20discussions%20of%20anti-NDA%20parties%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Seventeen%20parties%20gathered%20in%20Patna%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20July%2017-18.%20For%20Round%202%2C%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20expanded%20the%20list%20to%2024%20by%20including%20many%20smaller%20parties%20from%20the%20South.%20This%20window%20dressing%20by%20Kharge%20is%20designed%20to%20offset%20the%20BJP's%20bid%20to%20attract%20smaller%20parties%20in%20the%20North.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20meeting%20on%20July%2018%20in%20Delhi%20will%20feature%20the%20BJP's%20new%20Maharashtra%20allies%20-%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%20The%20return%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20to%20the%20NDA%20is%20being%20speculated.%20Karnataka's%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20(SBSP)%2C%20Bihar's%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20(VIP)%20and%20Hindustan%20Awami%20Morcha%20(HAM)%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Chirag%20Paswan%20faction%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%2C%20are%20also%20being%20brought%20in%20to%20widen%20the%20NDA's%20caste%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20line-ups%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20mosaic%20of%20India's%20multiparty%2C%20democratic%20politics.%20Addressing%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20stated%20India%20had%202%2C500%20political%20parties%20and%20about%2020%20different%20parties%20govern%20various%20states%20of%20India.%20Telangana's%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%2C%20Odisha's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20YSRCP%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20many%20parties%20with%20pockets%20of%20influence%20and%20vote%20banks%20are%20with%20neither%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru%20meet%2C%20like%20its%20Patna%20predecessor%2C%20will%20be%20an%20attempt%20by%20some%20-%20not%20all%20-%20opponents%20of%20the%20NDA%20to%20provide%20a%20united%20opposition%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bonus%20for%20Bengaluru%20is%20the%20announcement%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20will%20attend.%20She%20is%20the%20chairperson%20of%20UPA.%20In%202004%2C%20implementing%20her%20party's%202003%20Shimla%20Sankalp%2C%20she%20stitched%20together%20the%20UPA%20after%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20NDA%20rule%20crashed%20along%20with%20its%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Shining%26quot%3B%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20columnist%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopposition-unity-meet-confounded-by-when-and-where-4103104%5C%22%3Ehinted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20earlier%20despatch%20that%20the%20Congress%20intended%20to%20host%20the%20very%20first%20opposition%20meet%20in%20Shimla%20(prior%20to%20Patna%20being%20announced%20as%20the%20venue)%20to%20secure%20the%20presence%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20then%20recuperating%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20aversion%20of%20some%20parties%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20pivot%20of%20anti-BJP%20manoeuvres%20took%20the%20conclave%20to%20Patna.%20This%20reservation%20has%20not%20subsided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20has%20in%20the%20past%20formed%20alliances%20with%20ease.%20She%20is%20credited%20with%20ensuring%20that%20Congress%20did%20not%20wilt%20during%20her%20tenure%20as%20the%20longest-serving%20Congress%20president.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20present%20move%20has%20its%20origins%20in%20a%20meeting%20she%20had%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20September%20last.%20Leaders%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20are%20somewhat%20averse%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20feel%20comfortable%20with%20her.%20So%20do%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20are%20different%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20decades%20back%2C%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20was%20far%20healthier.%20CPI(M)%20secretary%20Harkishan%20Singh%20Surjeet%2C%20CPI's%20AB%20Bardhan%2C%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%20were%20the%20leaders%20who%20helped%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20network.%20Even%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20b%C3%AAte%20noire%2C%20VP%20Singh%2C%20stood%20with%20her%20to%20oust%20the%20BJP.%20An%20ailing%20Lalu%20Yadav%20is%20the%20only%20player%20of%202003%20active%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20Patel%2C%20Ambika%20Soni%20and%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20were%20her%20proactive%20aides%20who%20had%20wide%20contacts%20and%20persuasive%20skills.%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20Makhan%20Lal%20Fotedar%20and%20RK%20Dhawan%2C%20residues%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20era%2C%20also%20used%20their%20inter-party%20manoeuvring%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranab%2C%20Fotedar%20and%20Dhawan%20are%20no%20more.%20Ahmed%20Patel's%20death%20caused%20a%20vaccuum%20in%20the%20Congress%20that%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20filled.%20Azad%20has%20exited%20the%20party.%20Ambika%20Soni%20has%20not%20been%20active%20of%20late%2C%20though%20she%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20consultation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitaram%20Yechury%20is%20no%20Harkishan%20Surjeet.%20Nor%20are%20KC%20Venugopal%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20effective%20substitutes%20for%20Ahmed%20Patel%20and%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unity%20bid%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%202023%20is%20a%20closed%20group%20exercise%20assigned%20to%20Venugopal%20and%20his%20associates.%20Unlike%202003%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20used%20all%20possible%20resources%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20pivot%2C%20the%20party%20has%20a%20myopic%20approach%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20doubts%20circulating%20in%20the%20grapevine%20on%20the%20future%20moves%20of%20some%20of%20the%20participants%20of%20the%20meet.%20There%20are%20questions%20aplenty%20about%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20Patna%20meet%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20too.%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)'s%20Jayant%20Choudhry%2C%20currently%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20UP%2C%20skipped%20Patna%20but%20will%20join%20the%20Bengaluru%20meet.%20But%20there%20is%20talk%20that%20his%20party%20may%20be%20inclined%20towards%20realigning%20and%20may%20not%20stay%20in%20the%20anti-NDA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%20perceived%20as%20the%20patriarch%20of%20the%20anti-NDA%20lineup%2C%20is%20busy%20fighting%20bushfires%20in%20his%20own%20backyard.%20A%20section%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20when%20they%20met%20with%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20at%20the%20Congress%20headquarters%20to%20discuss%20political%20developments%20in%20their%20state%20on%20July%2011%2C%20raised%20red%20flags%20on%20Pawar%2C%20while%20sympathising%20with%20him%20against%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20are%20set%20to%20share%20a%20dais%20in%20Pune%20at%20a%20function%20to%20mark%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak's%20death%20anniversary.%20Modi%20is%20being%20given%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Award%20by%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Smarak%20Trust.%20It%20is%20a%20bipartisan%20event.%20A%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress's%20Maharashtra%20unit%2C%20Rohit%20Tilak%2C%20and%20veteran%20Congressman%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Shinde%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20memorial%20trust.%20Congress%20leaders%20from%20Maharashtra%20sounded%20an%20alarm%20on%20the%20Modi-Pawar%20event%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20has%20reiterated%20its%20demand%20that%20the%20Congress%20clarify%20its%20stand%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Ordinance%20before%20the%20Bengaluru%20talks.%20The%20very%20fact%20that%20AAP%20has%20been%20invited%20by%20Kharge%20shows%20that%20a%20final%20call%20has%20not%20been%20taken.%20The%20reservations%20of%20parties%20like%20AAP%20and%20suspicion%20within%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20motives%20of%20some%20participants%20are%20glitches%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20may%20need%20to%20paper%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20will%20be%20in%20Bengaluru%20after%20consolidating%20her%20home%20turf%20in%20the%20Panchayat%20elections.%20Will%20she%20be%20willing%20to%20play%20ball%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Left%20Front%20in%20West%20Bengal%20after%20this%20bitter%20rivalry%20in%20local%20polls%3F%20A%20three-way%20contest%20benefits%20her.%20This%2C%20and%20many%20more%20glitches%3B%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20inclination%20to%20go%20with%20the%20BRS%20and%20form%20a%20separate%20front%20altogether%20will%20be%20among%20the%20imponderables%20in%20the%20unity%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Bengaluru%20throw%20up%20a%20common%20agenda%3F%20Modi%20has%20floated%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20balloon.%20Will%20the%20Bengaluru%20participants%20have%20a%20common%20view%20on%20this%2C%20to%20begin%20with%3F%20To%20oppose%20the%20NDA%2C%20a%20refurbished%20UPA%2C%20if%20it%20emerges%2C%20will%20have%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20agenda%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689323160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fiuoha618_sonia-gandhi-ani-1200_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F2004-vs-2024-why-sonia-gandhi-may-not-help-opposition-efforts-4206640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unity%20bid%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%202023%20is%20a%20closed%20group%20exercise%20assigned%20to%20Venugopal%20and%20his%20associates.%20Unl