also%20provisions%20that%20are%20uniform%20across%20religions%20but%20not%20substantially%20equal%2C%20and%20there%20are%20also%20provisions%20that%20may%20be%20different%20but%20can%20enable%20empowerment%2C%20given%20our%20realities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20groups%E2%80%99%20statement%20reads%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fgoa-women-s-groups-call-for-justice-not-uniformity-in-response-to-uniform-civil-code-proposal-101689244023565.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20goalpost%20has%20to%20be%20justice%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20family%20and%20for%20all%20communities%2C%20rather%20than%20uniformity%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20one-month%20window%20for%20public%20consultation%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20the%20time%20period%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20suffice%20to%20deliberate%20on%20complex%20matters%20covering%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20areas%20such%20as%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20succession%2C%20guardianship%2C%20adoption%2C%20marital%20property%2C%20inheritance%2C%20different%20forms%20of%20property%2C%20and%20other%20related%20matters%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20%5Bhave%5D%20repercussions%20for%20us%20in%20Goa%2C%20for%20the%20whole%20country%20and%20for%20its%20diverse%20populations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-bobde-needs-to-know-that-goa-family-laws-are-not-at-all-uniform-or-equal%5C%22%3ECJI%20Bobde%20Needs%20to%20Know%20That%20Goa%20Family%20Laws%20Are%20Not%20All%20Uniform%20or%20Equal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCC%20is%20a%20proposed%20single%20set%20of%20laws%20that%20would%20uniformly%20govern%20personal%20matters%2C%20including%20marriage%2C%20divorce%20and%20inheritance%2C%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20different%20religious%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoa%20has%20its%20own%20uniform%20civil%20code%20that%20was%20enacted%20when%20it%20was%20under%20Portuguese%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20uniform%20code%20has%20elicited%20praise%20for%20being%20more%20%E2%80%9Cgender-just%E2%80%9D%20than%20similar%20laws%20in%20other%20states%2C%20and%20includes%20provisions%20enabling%20daughters%20to%20inherit%20equal%20shares%20of%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20properties%20and%20wives%20to%20inherit%20half%20a%20couple%E2%80%99s%20common%20assets%20following%20a%20divorce.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fabon%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAlbertina%20Almeida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20lawyer%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20collective%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%2C%20said%20that%20while%20there%20are%20fears%20that%20a%20UCC%20may%20not%20retain%20the%20positive%20aspects%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20uniform%20code%2C%20there%20is%20also%20uncertainty%20over%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20some%20of%20its%20sexist%20provisions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Flesson-goas-uniform-civil-code-uniformity-unjust-women-8817832%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20article%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Almeida%20wrote%20that%20the%20Goan%20civil%20code%20includes%20provisions%20that%20enable%20husbands%20to%20control%20how%20a%20couple%E2%80%99s%20matrimonial%20property%20is%20managed%20and%20dispose%20of%20such%20property%20without%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20consent%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Goan%20civil%20code%2C%20%E2%80%98matrimonial%20property%E2%80%99%20includes%20property%20that%20either%20spouse%20purchased%20or%20inherited%20before%20the%20subsistence%20of%20their%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmeida%20also%20wrote%20that%20the%20Code%20of%20Usages%20and%20Customs%20of%20Gentile%20Hindus%2C%20a%20law%20that%20is%20part%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20overall%20set%20of%20family%20laws%2C%20sanctions%20patriarchs%20to%20govern%20and%20manage%20a%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20undivided%20family%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20provides%20for%20polygamy%20and%20adoption%20under%20sexist%20terms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-clamour-for-uniform-civil-code-driven-by-aim-of-dividing-not-uniting-indians%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Clamour%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Driven%20by%20Aim%20of%20Dividing%2C%20Not%20Uniting%2C%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fpatriarchy-and-property-rights-goas-uniform-civil-code%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20under%20the%20Code%20of%20Usages%2C%20a%20Hindu%20male%20can%20marry%20a%20second%20time%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20without%20divorcing%20the%20first%20wife%20in%20case%20no%20child%20is%20born%20by%20the%20time%20she%20attains%20the%20age%20of%2025%2C%20if%20no%20male%20child%20is%20born%20to%20the%20first%20wife%20when%20she%20attains%20the%20age%20of%2030%20years%20and%20if%20there%20is%20a%20ten-year%20gap%20between%20pregnancies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20collective%20statement%20by%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20once%20again%20pushes%20for%20a%20nationwide%20UCC.%20Late%20last%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-poll-bound-madhya-pradesh-pm-modi-rakes-up-triple-talaq-ucc-and-appeasement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebrought%20up%20the%20UCC%20during%20a%20speech%20in%20Bhopal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20he%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20personal%20laws%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmeida%20said%20that%20cherry-picking%20the%20personal%20laws%20of%20certain%20communities%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20UCC%20creates%20a%20rhetoric%20that%20is%20ultimately%20harmful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20atmosphere%20has%20to%20be%20created%20for%20people%20to%20articulate%20the%20challenges%20they%20face%20in%20accessing%20the%20law%20or%20because%20of%20the%20law%2C%20which%20cannot%20easily%20happen%20within%20a%20rhetoric%20where%20laws%20of%20a%20section%20of%20society%20are%20cherry-picked%20for%20critique.%20This%20kind%20of%20attitude%20can%20only%20drive%20women%20and%20marginal%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20family%20to%20silence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689318640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F04101723%2FScreenshot-2022-05-04-at-10.17.19-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgoan-womens-groups-urge-justice-over-uniformity-in-a-ucc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20there%20are%20fears%20that%20a%20UCC%20may%20not%20retain%20the%20positive%20aspects%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20own%20uniform%20code%2C%20there%20is%20also%20uncertainty%20over%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20some%20of%20the%20latter's%20sexist%20provisions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A