20aspect%20of%20Indian%20weddings%20is%20the%20gifts.%20While%20going%20through%20her%20attic%2C%20Anupama%20found%20a%20huge%20bundle%20of%20butter%20paper%20which%20she%20had%20stowed%20away%20after%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20thread%20ceremony%20in%202004.%20She%20used%20that%20to%20pack%20the%20gifts%20for%20the%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20gave%20everyone%20naturally%20dyed%20blouse%20pieces.%20Even%20if%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stitch%20it%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20someone%20else.%20I%20also%20used%20all%20the%20%3Cem%3Earishina%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ekumkuma%20(turmeric%20and%20vermillion%20powder)%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20I%20had%20at%20home%20and%20packed%20them%20in%20papers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20used%20only%20fresh%20flowers%20for%20decorations.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20friends%20sent%20the%20flowers%20to%20a%20studio%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20used%20them%20as%20natural%20dyes%20and%20created%20clothes%20for%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Vasuki%20Iyengar%20%E2%80%93%20DIY%20Guy%20(%40vasuki.composting)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mothers%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20easier%20to%20plan%20a%20no-plastic%20wedding.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20easier%20and%20cleaner.%20There%20is%20no%20waste%20lying%20around.%20The%20venue%20was%20clean%20all%20the%20time.%20One%20just%20needs%20to%20have%20the%20will%20to%20live%20a%20plastic-free%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20each%20wedding%20%3Cem%3Emandap%3C%2Fem%3E%20starts%20having%20a%20dishwasher%2C%20so%20much%20waste%20can%20be%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20have%20a%20cutlery%20bank%20of%2050-100%20utensils%20amongst%20your%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20and%20circulate%20it%20around.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20how%20our%20mothers%20and%20grandmothers%20lived%3F%20My%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296376%2Fplan-ecofriendly-green-wedding-zero-waste-ideas-vendors-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20was%20effortlessly%20plastic-free%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20all%20events%20were%20conducted%20during%20my%20time.%20Today%2C%20we%20need%20to%20highlight%20such%20an%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnupama%20and%20Charulatha%20inspire%20us%20to%20go%20back%20to%20living%20naturally%2C%20like%20our%20mothers%20and%20grandmothers%20did%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgroundreport.in%2Fenvironmental-cost-of-the-big-fat-indian-wedding%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520average%2520Indian%2520wedding%2520generates%2C14%2520billion%2520worth%2520of%2520meals.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Environmental%20Cost%20of%20The%20Big%20Fat%20Indian%20Wedding%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Palak%20Tripathi%20for%20Ground%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689316963000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmoms1-min-1689255976.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20mothers%20Anupama%20Harish%20and%20Charulatha%20R%20hosted%20a%20low-waste%20plastic-free%20wedding%20for%20their%20children%20that%20lasted%20three%20days.%20From%20using%20eco-friendly%20decor%20and%20steel%20utensils%20to%20arrangements%20for%20food%20waste%20to%20be%20composted%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20did%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Mercy%20for%20the%20Vulnerable%20as%20Authorities%20Beautified%20Urban%20Areas%20for%20G20%20Events%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14115734%2FScreenshot-2023-07-14-at-11.51.0.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20report%20collating%20testimonies%20of%20those%20affected%20by%20forced%20evictions%20purportedly%20necessitated%20by%20India%20hosting%20the%20G20%20summit%20has%20unveiled%20a%20picture%20of%20particular%20administrative%20apathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20compiled%20and%20released%20by%20the%20group%2C%20Concerned%20Citizens%20of%20India%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20in%20an%20event%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewas%20addressed%20by%20senior%20journalist%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20ombudsperson%20Pamela%20Philipose%2C%20rights%20activist%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20former%20Deputy%20Mayor%20of%20Shimla%20Tikender%20Panwar%20and%20community%20leaders%20Shakeel%20Abdul%20and%20Akbar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20May%20a%20public%20hearing%20was%20held%20in%20which%20representatives%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20Indore%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20apart%20from%20different%20slum%20colonies%20in%20Delhi%2C%20spoke%20the%20alleged%20brutality%20inflicted%20upon%20communities%20which%20were%20evicted%20by%20authorities%20with%20the%20G20%20events%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20observes%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%E2%80%98distressing%E2%80%99%20instances%20of%20%3Cspan%3Eforced%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eevictions%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20was%20covered%20at%20the%20public%20hearing%20was%20the%20demolition%20of%20homeless%20shelters%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-photos-for-g20-beautification-poor-families-living-along-the-yamuna-face-eviction%5C%22%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20Yamuna%20Pushta%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Urban%20Shelter%20Improvement%20Board%3Cbr%3E%5Cndemolished%20eight%20of%20its%20own%20shelters%20near%20the%20Yamuna%20floodplains%2C%20leaving%20the%20homeless%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20live%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20report%20says%20that%20a%20shelter%20at%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%20has%20also%20been%20removed%20apparently%20because%20a%20park%20has%20been%20constructed%20nearby%20%E2%80%93%20a%20venue%20to%20which%20%3Cspan%3EG20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20dignitaries%20will%20be%20brought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-india-prepares-to-host-g20-meet-delhis-most-vulnerable-have-been-rendered-homeless%5C%22%3EAs%20India%20Prepares%20to%20Host%20G20%20Meet%2C%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Vulnerable%20Have%20Been%20Rendered%20Homeless%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20information%20takes%20on%20new%20significance%20with%20the%20Yamuna%20swelling%20to%20record%20heights%20and%2C%20resultantly%2C%20flooding%20parts%20of%20Delhi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20quotes%20Seema%2C%20a%20disabled%20mother%20whose%20living%20quarters%20in%20the%20shelter%20was%20destroyed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20supply%20has%20also%20been%20stopped.%20Now%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20living%20under%20trees.%20I%20cannot%20move%20since%20%5Bmy%5D%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20family%20loads%20their%20belongings%20on%20a%20cart%20in%20case%20the%20bulldozers%20arrive.%20Photo%3A%20Shome%20Basu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20time%20between%20a%20notice%20and%20the%20demolition%20drive%20was%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPuja%20from%20Bela%20Estate%20in%20Delhi%20also%20noted%20that%20demolishers%20broke%20the%20hand%20pumps%20so%20that%20they%20could%20leave%20within%20the%20three-hour%20window%20they%20were%20given%20to%20pack%20their%20things.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20students%20missed%20their%20board%E2%80%99s%20exam%20due%20to%20the%20eviction%20that%20took%20place%20on%2029th%20April%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20that%20even%20the%20Delhi%20urban%20minister%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20drive%20and%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20CEO%20of%20DUSIB.%20After%20this%2C%20a%20new%20law%20was%20promulgated%20under%20which%20demolitions%20of%20shelters%20can%20only%20take%20place%20under%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShakeel%20Abdul%20from%20Basti%20Suraksha%20Manch%20said%20250%2C000%20to%20300%2C000%20people%20were%20forcibly%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20floodplains%2C%20Tughlaqabad%2C%20and%20Bela%20state%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%3EG20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20erection%20of%20barricades%20also%20cut%20off%20access%20roads%20to%20these%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESucheta%20De%2C%20an%20activist%2C%20is%20quoted%20in%20the%20report%20as%20having%20said%20that%20Tuglaqabad%20looks%20as%20if%20%E2%80%9Can%20aerial%20bombardment%20has%20taken%20place%2C%20given%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20destruction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20noted%20how%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20G20%20inauguration%20meant%20that%20slums%20were%20being%20hidden%20behind%20iron%20sheets%20covered%20with%20plastic%20grass%20so%20that%20they%20appear%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%E2%80%9D.%20The%20city%E2%80%99s%20police%20commissioner%20issued%20a%20public%20order%20that%20no%20beggars%20must%20be%20visible%20at%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20crossroads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Visakhapatnam%2C%205.5-foot%20tall%20green%20sheets%20extending%20for%20about%20400%20metres%20were%20been%20put%20up%20allegedly%20by%20civic%20authorities%20to%20cover%20the%20shanties%20of%20over%20100%20tribal%20families%20in%20ASR%20Nagar.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20living%20there%20belong%20to%20the%20Chenchu%20tribe%2C%20classified%20as%20a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Ironically%2C%20G20%20delegates%20in%20the%20city%20discussed%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%98Financing%20Cities%20of%20Tomorrow%3A%20Inclusive%2C%20Resilient%20and%20Sustainable.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20out%20a%20moment%20for%20mindfulness!%20%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%80%8D%E2%99%80%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%80%8D%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FG20%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23G20%3C%2Fa%3E%20delegates%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FVisakhapatnam%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Visakhapatnam%3C%2Fa%3E%20kicked%20off%20their%20day%20with%20a%20rejuvenating%20and%20holistic%20experience%2C%20as%20they%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20ancient%20practices%20of%20yoga%20and%20meditation.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FG20India%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23G20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIWG%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref