Mahotsav%2C%20existing%20literature%20has%20to%20be%20translated%20in%20different%20Indian%20languages.%20At%20least%2075%20Universities%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20this%20activity%20over%20next%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20documents%20accessed%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUGC%20(the%20University%20Grants%20Commission)%20and%20Bureau%20Heads%20are%20requested%20to%20mobilise%20Universities%2FAutonomous%20Organisations%2C%20under%20their%20administrative%20control%2C%20in%20this%20exercise%20and%20keep%20this%20Division%20informed%20of%20the%20activities%20being%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20office%20memorandum%20was%20forwarded%20to%20all%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20IIMs%2C%20under%20the%20ministry%20in%20November%202021%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20IIM%20Bangalore%2C%20IIM%20Kashipur%20and%20IIM%20Udaipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fiims-snub-union-ministry-over-diktat-on-translation-of-existing-literature%2Fcid%2F1951905%5C%22%3Ewrote%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20the%20order%20was%20not%20applicable%20to%20them%2C%20the%20remaining%2017%20have%20not%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIMB%20is%20a%20Management%20Institute.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20literature%20for%20translation%20into%20other%20languages%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20of%20IIM%20Bangalore%20in%20an%20email%20to%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%20Udaipur%E2%80%99s%20then%20director%2C%20Janat%20Shah%2C%20wrote%20back%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20translation%20of%20existing%20literature%20by%20Universities%20(using%20AICTE%20translation%20tools)%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20IIM%20Udaipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%20Kashipur%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20M.%20Ramasubramanian%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20respect%20to%20the%20training%20email%2C%20this%20is%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20IIM%20Kashipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Council%20for%20Technical%20Education%20(AICTE)%20is%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20translate%20literature%20in%20existing%20subjects%20to%20local%20languages%20as%20IITs%20and%20NITs%20are%20also%20being%20persuaded%20to%20offer%20their%20courses%20in%20Indian%20languages%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689309057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiims-oppose-union-governments-diktat-to-translate-syllabus-into-local-languages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20education%20ministry%20had%20issued%20an%20office%20memorandum%20in%202021%20asking%20at%20least%2075%20institutions%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20exercise%20as%20part%20of%20'Azadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiims-oppose-union-governments-diktat-to-translate-syllabus-into-local-languages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fran%20Drescher%20Takes%20Center%20Stage%20in%20Hollywood%20Labor%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689308702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSAG-Actors-Strike-Fran-Drescher.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235670210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20clock%20ticked%20toward%20midnight%20on%20July%2012%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20president%20Fran%20Drescher%20addressed%20the%20group%20of%20negotiators%20from%20t