ay%20became%20confined%20to%20his%20home.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20look%20for%20something%20to%20do%20in%20my%20free%20time%20and%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20various%20things.%20What%20I%20noticed%20was%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20getting%20into%20baking%20and%20confectionery.%20This%20seemed%20doable%2C%20and%20I%20have%20always%20been%20an%20ardent%20chocolate%20lover%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20shared%20this%20idea%20with%20my%20cousin%20Mahaveer%20Singh%20and%20he%20was%20enthusiastic%20to%20join%20me.%20However%2C%20back%20then%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20plan%20of%20action.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20how%20to%20make%20chocolates%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20always%20had%20a%20curious%20mind%20and%20loved%20learning%20new%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20YouTube%2C%20Digvijay%20learnt%20the%20art%20of%20making%20chocolates%20and%20started%20to%20distribute%20them%20to%20family%20and%20friends%20to%20try.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20keep%20practising%20and%20moving%20between%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F245585%2Fat-21-he-started-selling-momos-from-his-home-kitchen-now-has-rs-180-cr-turnover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20my%20home%20kitchen%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20my%20aunt%E2%80%99s%20kitchen.%20There%20have%20been%20errors%20too%2C%20but%20with%20time%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20right%20balance.%20Initially%2C%20I%20was%20funding%20it%20myself%20with%20the%20money%20I%20earned%20from%20a%20part-time%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20were%20not%20really%20aware%20of%20the%20plan%20I%20had%20and%20they%20probably%20looked%20at%20it%20as%20a%20hobby.%20When%20I%20received%20good%20reviews%20from%20my%20parents%20and%20friends%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20a%20business%20plan.%E